### LOGIN - Get JWT Token (Use this first!)
POST http://localhost:8080/academics/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123"
}
> {%
    // Guarda o token automaticamente para ser usado nos pedidos
    client.global.set("auth_token", response.body);
%}

### Get authenticated user (replace <JWT_TOKEN> with the token returned above)
GET http://localhost:8080/academics/api/auth/user
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
